Add three location blocks to `/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/scanner.taifoon.dev` BEFORE the catch-all `^~ /api/`:
```
location ^~ /api/ollama/ {
    rewrite ^/api/ollama/(.*)$ /$1 break;
    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:11434;
    proxy_buffering off;
}
location = /api/llm/health {
    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/tags;
}
location ^~ /api/llm/ {
    rewrite ^/api/llm/(.*)$ /api/$1 break;
    proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:11434;
    proxy_buffering off;
}
```
Then `nginx -t && systemctl reload nginx`. With nginx's `^~` modifier the longest-prefix wins, so `/api/ollama/` (11 chars) and `/api/llm/` (8) match before `/api/` (5). Verified 2026-04-25: both endpoints return 200 with the live models JSON. Other agents should call `https://scanner.taifoon.dev/api/llm/health` for liveness and `/api/ollama/api/generate` for inference.
